# Grammar for "the man shot the soldier with a gun"
# PP attachment is ambiguous (VP-attach vs NP-attach)
1.0   S    NP VP
0.5   NP   DT N
0.3   NP   DT N PP
0.2   NP   N
0.5   VP   V NP
0.5   VP   V NP PP
1.0   PP   P NP
0.3   DT   the
0.3   DT   a
0.4   DT   an
1.0   N    man
0.5   N    soldier
0.5   N    gun
1.0   V    shot
1.0   P    with
